With this you could define [running elements][2] as defined in the CSS 3 specification.

So you could define a footer element within your gsp:

    &lt;body&gt;
        ...
        &lt;div id=&quot;footer&quot;&gt;Your Watermark&lt;/div&gt;
        ...
    &lt;/body&gt;

And style it like this:

    &lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
        @page {
            size: 210mm 297mm;
            @bottom-right {content: element(footer)};
            ...
        }
        
        #footer{
            position: running(footer);
        }

        ...
    &lt;/style&gt;


